[Episode 4: Move, you darned time machine!]

293
00:16:31,000 --> 00:16:33,400
It's fine; I'm good at cleaning.

294
00:16:34,240 --> 00:16:36,580
All right!

295
00:16:36,580 --> 00:16:39,150
- Mind if I tidy up this space?
- Sure.

296
00:16:39,150 --> 00:16:42,270
Just don't push yourself, okay?
I don't mind the mess.

297
00:16:42,270 --> 00:16:44,740
Well, I do.

298
00:16:44,740 --> 00:16:48,200
- Dinner is served.
- Wow! Amazing!

299
00:16:51,340 --> 00:16:53,600
- That's delicious!
- Really? I'm glad to hear it.

300
00:16:54,510 --> 00:16:57,610
- Thanks for cooking such a feast.
- No problem.

301
00:16:57,610 --> 00:16:59,440
