- Oh, Gen-chan!

328
00:18:29,420 --> 00:18:31,920
Long time no see!

329
00:18:31,920 --> 00:18:32,990
- Are you heading in here?
- Yes.

330
00:18:32,990 --> 00:18:34,870
- Me, too.
- Seriously?

331
00:18:34,870 --> 00:18:36,840
Minato is...

332
00:18:36,840 --> 00:18:39,860
He's quick to start dating
and quick to break up, too.

333
00:18:39,860 --> 00:18:43,180
A mass consumption lover boy.

334
00:18:52,870 --> 00:18:55,410
- Hey, long time no see!
- What's up, Man?

335
00:18:55,410 --> 00:18:57,310
How's it going?

336
00:19:00,280 --> 00:19:03,210
What in the world am I doing?

337
00:19:04,890 --> 00:19:06,460
Ayu-chan!

338
00:19:06,460 --> 00:19:08,060
Oh, Minato-san.

339
00:19:08,060 --> 00:19:09,440
- You were here?
- Yes.

340
00:19:09,440 --> 00:19:12,380
- When did you arrive?
- A little while ago.

341
00:19:12,380 --> 00:19:13,550
- Really?
- Yes.

342
00:19:13,550 --> 00:19:15,220
Want to dance with me, Ayu-chan?

343
00:19:15,220 --> 00:19:17,580
"Dance"? Her? Are you joking?

344
00:19:17,580 --> 00:19:20,350
She would never.

345
00:19:20,350 --> 00:19:22,900
- I'd love to!
- All right!

346
00:19:22,900 --> 00:19:25,400
Everyone, this is Ayu-chan!

347
00:19:25,400 --> 00:19:28,020
- Hey, Ayu-chan.
- Nice to meet you.

348
00:19:28,020 --> 00:19:29,820
Great to have you here.

349
00:19:39,640 --> 00:19:42,420
- Your tequila.
- Wow, nice.

350
00:19:42,420 --> 00:19:43,330
- Thank you.
- Thanks.

351
00:19:43,330 --> 00:19:45,500
Ayumi would never drink tequila.

352
00:19:45,500 --> 00:19:47,960
Cheers!

353
00:19:50,900 --> 00:19:52,250
Delicious!

354
00:19:52,250 --> 00:19:57,370
I'm telling you, that guy is no good...

355
00:19:57,370 --> 00:20:00,400
Want to dance a bit more, Ayu-chan?

356
00:20:01,460 --> 00:20:05,040
How about we eat dinner together at home?

357
00:20:05,040 --> 00:20:06,530
Hey, it's Minato.

358
00:20:06,530 --> 00:20:09,760
- Minato!
- Sumi-chan! Ko-chan!

359
00:20:09,760 --> 00:20:12,130
- Long time no see.
- Hey there.

360
00:20:12,130 --> 00:20:15,230
You know, just the other day
we were talking about you.

361
00:20:15,230 --> 00:20:18,470
Yes, a person practically
interrogated us about you.

362
00:20:18,470 --> 00:20:22,560
- What?
- Yes, they were super interested in you.

363
00:20:22,560 --> 00:20:25,630
- Say, why don't you join us for a drink?
- Sounds good.

364
00:20:25,630 --> 00:20:28,610
Oh, right. Want to join us, Ayu-chan?

365
00:20:29,570 --> 00:20:31,470
Yes, drink with us!

366
00:20:31,470 --> 00:20:35,150
- I'll tell you all about Minato's past.
- Girl, stop that!

367
00:20:35,150 --> 00:20:37,720
Don't say silly things.

368
00:20:42,870 --> 00:20:44,400
Actually, I think I'll head home.

369
00:20:44,400 --> 00:20:46,390
- Already?
- Yes.

370
00:20:46,390 --> 00:20:49,200
- Okay. Take care on your way back then.
- Sure.

371
00:20:50,340 --> 00:20:52,360
Minato-san.

372
00:20:52,360 --> 00:20:53,700
Yes?

373
00:20:58,770 --> 00:21:01,000
I'll wait for you back at home, okay?

374
00:21:01,000 --> 00:21:03,200
Okay.

375
00:21:04,810 --> 00:21:06,970
Could I get a check, please?

376
00:21:06,970 --> 00:21:08,710
- It's fine, drinks are on me tonight.
- You sure?

377
00:21:08,710 --> 00:21:10,330
Of course.

378
00:21:23,870 --> 00:21:26,170
They're living together.

379
00:21:29,800 --> 00:21:32,120
They're already living together.

380
00:22:00,300 --> 00:22:03,680
I've never seen Ayumi
enjoy herself like that before.

381
00:22:09,180 --> 00:22:12,310
Did she ever laugh like that with me?

382
00:22:39,940 --> 00:22:45,970
[Katsuo-san]

383
00:22:55,370 --> 00:22:59,600
Oh, I messed up. This is bad. I overslept.

384
00:22:59,600 --> 00:23:01,310
I won't make it to first period.

385
00:23:01,310 --> 00:23:02,780
Hey.

386
00:23:02,780 --> 00:23:04,690
You start class at second period, right?

387
00:23:04,690 --> 00:23:06,630
How about we skip class today?

388
00:23:09,870 --> 00:23:12,040
I suppose we have enough credits to make do.

389
00:23:21,440 --> 00:23:23,630
That smells great.

390
00:23:23,630 --> 00:23:25,060
It's almost done.

391
00:23:25,060 --> 00:23:26,800
What're you cooking?

392
00:23:26,800 --> 00:23:28,240
It's a surprise.

393
00:23:28,240 --> 00:23:31,550
- Ta-da.
- I feel like I'm eating at a restaurant.

394
00:23:31,550 --> 00:23:34,100
- Wow!
- Is it that impressive?

395
00:23:34,100 --> 00:23:35,930
Absolutely. This looks amazing.

396
00:23:35,930 --> 00:23:38,070
- Can I try a bite?
- Wait a second.

397
00:23:38,070 --> 00:23:40,580
Can I squeeze a heart in?
[Katsuo-san]

398
00:23:40,580 --> 00:23:42,840
- There.
- No way.

399
00:23:42,840 --> 00:23:44,900
This is adorable.

400
00:23:44,900 --> 00:23:46,360
Hold on.

401
00:23:47,750 --> 00:23:49,720
I have to take a picture.

402
00:23:49,720 --> 00:23:51,740
This isn't anything photo-worthy.

403
00:23:51,740 --> 00:23:53,390
Of course it is. It's your cooking.

404
00:23:53,390 --> 00:23:54,920
You're overreacting.

405
00:23:54,920 --> 00:23:57,520
You have many more
homemade meals to come, you know?

406
00:24:00,030 --> 00:24:02,450
There.

407
00:24:02,450 --> 00:24:05,840
- Thanks for the meal.
- Of course.

408
00:24:09,370 --> 00:24:12,240
Wow, that's delicious!

409
00:24:12,240 --> 00:24:14,440
This is fantastic.

410
00:24:40,450 --> 00:24:43,940
Cheers!

411
00:24:47,790 --> 00:24:49,530
Should we get drinking?

412
00:24:49,530 --> 00:24:51,220
- Drink up!
- Let's drink this place dry!

413
00:24:51,220 --> 00:24:53,250
I'm down!

414
00:24:55,170 --> 00:24:57,630
No. It doesn't bother me at all.

415
00:24:58,930 --> 00:25:04,720
A good woman doesn't fret over small things.

416
00:25:06,890 --> 00:25:11,460
Oh? Am I enduring again?

417
00:25:21,610 --> 00:25:25,160
[Minato-san: I'll be late today.
Feel free to go to sleep.]

418
00:25:27,180 --> 00:25:30,280
He might come home hungry.

419
00:25:56,310 --> 00:25:58,400
I want to eat it.

420
00:26:02,830 --> 00:26:04,900
I want him to eat this.

421
