00:26:18,830 --> 00:26:20,750
♫ I was fed up ♫

423
00:26:20,750 --> 00:26:21,780
I want him to eat this.

424
00:26:21,780 --> 00:26:24,460
♫ Where did we go wrong? ♫

425
00:26:24,460 --> 00:26:27,740
♫ Our ideals are drifting apart ♫

426
00:26:27,740 --> 00:26:30,850
♫ And we can no longer accept each other ♫

427
00:26:30,850 --> 00:26:33,870
♫ Ridiculously, we are ♫

428
00:26:34,820 --> 00:26:38,400
I want Minato-san to eat my cooking.

429
00:26:40,400 --> 00:26:43,750
I want to eat Ayumi's omurice*.
(*Omelet rice)

430
00:26:43,750 --> 00:26:48,420
♫ I gradually improved at playing along with you ♫

431
00:26:48,420 --> 00:26:50,400
Bon appétit.

432
00:26:51,570 --> 00:26:55,540
♫ I lost sight of myself ♫

433
00:26:55,540 --> 00:27:01,060
♫ To the point that there's no room
to discuss the old-fashioned ideas ♫

434
00:27:01,060 --> 00:27:04,010
♫ What we lacked ♫

435
00:27:04,010 --> 00:27:06,060
♫ Wasn't ideals ♫

436
00:27:06,060 --> 00:27:09,750
♫ Notice the warm honesty ♫

437
