[Katsuo]
♫ Notice the warm honesty ♫

438
00:27:12,100 --> 00:27:17,820
♫ That changes through our clumsy love ♫

439
00:27:17,820 --> 00:27:19,820
[Minato-san]
♫ Not everyone can live cleverly ♫

440
00:27:19,820 --> 00:27:24,840
♫ Not everyone can live cleverly ♫

